title: The Great Bongo Heist
description: The boys forget to get Chata a gift for Abuela Day and in a panicked move, they pretend that the bongo drums they borrowed from Xochi are for her. Knowing they have to return the drums, Victor & Valentino pretend to be burglars to steal the bongos back.

title: Elements Part 7: Hero Heart
description: A full-scale war has broken out between two kingdoms and it's up to Ooo's most unlikely hero to stop it!

title: Manlier Fish the Fishlier Man
description: With the help of a conch shell genie, Man Fish upgrades himself in various ways to defeat the Warriors.

title: Save the Date
description: Ms. Keane is nervous about a first date.

title: Banana Joe
description: Cuando el director Brown le asigna a Darwin la tarea de hacer el anuario escolar, Darwin comienza pidiéndole a Banana Joe, el payaso de la clase, una simple selfi para la portada. Pero con Banana Joe, las cosas nunca son tan simples.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Falafel's in Jail
description: Apple & Onion must get Falafel out of jail for a crime he did not commit.

title: Efecto Entrega
description: Unikitty y su banda pidieron una deliciosa comida tailandesa para la cena. Por desgracia, la espera para la entrega se está haciendo demasiado larga y hasta el tiempo parece pasar más lento. En un esfuerzo por conseguir la comida más rápido, la banda utiliza la máquina del tiempo de la Dra. Fox, lo cual causa graves problemas y hiere profundamente los sentimientos del Padre Tiempo.

title: Planet X
description: When Rad returns to his home planet, he learns a shocking truth about alien society.

title: The Pressure
description: Gumball tries to save Darwin from being kissed by a girl.

title: Camp Unikitty
description: The gang's set for an awesome weekend of glamorous, easy-living camping out in fun, friendly nature! But when Hawkodile challenges their idea of camping (it should be a fight for survival in the hostile woods), the gang switch places, with Hawkodile living a luxurious glamp life while Unikitty and the others survive in the wild. Will Unikitty still believe the "great outdoors" are all that great if they meet their doom by natural causes?

title: Ant We All Just Get Along
description: Owen and Beth try to save an ant hill that Courtney and Leshawna want to destroy.

title: Final Battle! Dan vs. Ajit/Secrets Exposed
description: Final Battle! Dan vs. Ajit: It's time for the event everyone in Los Volmos has been waiting for, The Bakugan Battle League finals! It's the Awesome Brawler's Dan Kouzo vs. the golden Bakugan brawler Ajit, these two face-off in a final brawl for it all./Secrets Exposed: The Bakugan Battle League has ended, and the winner has been determined, but the celebration is cut short when Phantom Thief Storm crashes the party by stealing everyone's Bakugan! It's up to Dan and Ajit to stop Storm and return all the stolen Bakugan.

title: Elements Part 8: Skyhooks II
description: With time running out, Finn and Lumpy Space Princess work together to unlock one of Ooo's greatest secrets.

title: Prankless
description: The guys want to win a prank war with a rival park.

title: Alone Quest
description: Craig has an "emergency" leaving Kelsey alone at the Stump.

title: While You Were Away
description: Dr. Psychobos and Princess Attea have invaded Rook's home planet Revonnah with an army of Incurseans! (Introducing new Ben alien, Astrodactyl.)

title: Vilgax Must Croak
description: Ben and Rook escort Vilgax to a maximum-security prison planet, but the Incurseans have other plans. (Introducing Eighteight.)

title: Communicate Openly
description: Bumbleebee becomes the 6th Titan and moves into the Tower but has a hard time adjusting.

title: Hand Zombie
description: After Starfire kisses his hand, Robin vows to never wash it again.

title: Letter Wronging Campaign
description: When Prohyas sends Vambre for a much needed spa day, he drafts Noville to help on a mission to discover why all the books in the Library of Shhhhh are blank.

title: The Potato
description: When Darwin has lunch with Idaho, he decides to stop eating potatoes in solidarity with his brotato. However, he finds his obsession with his favourite food harder to kick than he ever imagined so Gumball decides to help his friend curb his carb cravings.

title: #MisgivingTree
description: Jessica Cruz and Pam Isley bond over protecting an ancient tree from being cut down. Neither of them realizes who the other's alter ego is, or the lengths to which they'll go to protect what's important.

title: Together Alone
description: Steven throws a party to bring his family together.

title: Costume Contest
description: Sick of losing the costume contest to the Hive Five every year, the Titans hatch a scheme to win.

title: The Mystery of the Timekeeper
description: When the Time Keeper goes missing, Craig and his friends take up the task of helping kids get home in time for dinner.

title: Hostile Take Over/The Big Bounce
description: Hostile Take Over: After more unsuccessful attempts to harness Core Cell energy the AO must battle their own Bakugan with AAAnimus tech in order to save them./The Big Bounce: The AO confront Philomena with concerns about her control over the Core Cell energy and are fired in the most unceremonious of manners.

title: Fiesta de Monstruos
description: Enid debe tomar una decisión cuando llegan sus antiguos amigos de la Escuela de monstruos.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: The Bad Guy Busters
description: Izzy wants to play a superhero game and is willing to do whatever it takes to get the others to see it through.

title: The Big Game
description: Chad takes Clarence to his first big game! Clarence takes it all in - the crack of the bat, the touchdown dances, the slam-dunks and of course, hotdogs and popcorn! But will Clarence get to fulfill his dream of meeting Aberdale's beloved mascot?

title: Mr. Gus Moves Out
description: When a fed-up Mr. Gus moves out of the RV, Uncle Grandpa and Pizza Steve work together to get him back.

title: Fragments
description: Steven heads to the woods to train with a powerful mentor.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Lightfall Part 2
description: Lord Obsidian attacks the Lighthouse, but Mega Man overcomes his insecurity and works with his family to repel the big bad, who's rescued at the last second by a mysterious lieutenant, Namagem.

title: Lad & Logic
description: KO learns the story of how Mr. Logic came to the plaza.

title: Cambia de Parecer
description: Steven se enfrenta al mayor desafío de su vida.

title: Speed Demon/Mojo Jonesin'
description: Mojo Jonesin':  When the children of Pokey Oaks become envious of the girls' superpowers, a mysterious figure offers them Chemical X. Now, the girls must fight their own classmates who have powers equal to their own./Speed Demon: The girls accidentally fly at the speed of light and when they arrive home, everything has changed. Fifty years have passed and the world has been taken over by Him.

title: Party Down Part 2
description: A malfunction in Wheeljack's party favors turns most of the Autobot crew feral, leaving Optimus, Cheetor, and Teletraan-X in a race to save their friends.

title: Vreedlemania
description: Pa Vreedle reunites with Ma for all-out destruction.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Triquicornio
description: Un misterioso pariente, el tío Triquicornio, aparece inesperadamente asegurando ser de la familia. Halcondrilo cree que solo son Master Frown y Brock en un disfraz de burro tratando de arruinar las cosas, pero Unikitty y Perricornio están convencidos de que Triquicornio en un viejo miembro de la familia. Halcondrilo sigue sus instintos de guardaespaldas e intenta probar que Triquicornio es un impostor.

title: Worm Bin
description: After his mom gets a worm bin, Jeff deals with the gross reality that he has a tub of bugs living in his kitchen, and Clarence obsesses over feeding the worms.

title: Wild Wild Wheel Part 1
description: A dangerous lone gunslinger named WildWheel returns to Cybertron looking for Optimus Prime.

title: Prank Callers
description: Mordecai and Rigby try and prank the Master Prank Caller to be the best prank callers. The MPC sends them back to 1982.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Despedidos
description: Los Fantásticos confrontan a Filomena, preocupados de que ella controle la energía de la Célula núcleo, y son despedidos de una forma poco profesional.

title: La ofensiva de Encantos
description: Cuando Ben recibe demasiada publicidad por sus travesuras alienígenas en Fort Knox, Gwen se pone celosa, se siente poco apreciada, y busca aliviar su dolor con helado. Pero cuando Charmcaster la confronta con la intención de vengar a Michael Morningstar, Gwen debe demostrarse a sí misma que es un miembro digno del equipo Tennyson si quiere sobrevivir.

title: Elements Part 6: Happy Warrior
description: One step closer to success, Finn and his friends fight through a new, more brutal, Fire Kingdom to find Flame Princess.

title: Everything's Fine
description: Steven insists that everything is fine.

title: Game of Masks
description: As Lloyd and Harumi search the Oni Temple for the last mask, the ninja are taken hostage and discover Princess Harumi's true intentions.

title: True Potential
description: Just when the Ninja think they have saved the day, Lord Garmadon returns to Ninjago, and frees Harumi, who encourages him to "achieve his true potential" by conquering the one thing that has always stood in his way, his son, Lloyd.

title: Mision solitaria
description: Craig debe atender una "emergencia", dejando a Kelsey sola en el Tronco.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Double Hex
description: While bird watching at Pinnacles National Park, Gwen and Ben get into a competition of who can spot more birds first, but once a forest fire interrupts their fun, Team Tennyson must hurry if they are to save the bird population and discover who is behind the suspiciously growing fire: Hex!

title: Booby-Traps, and How To Survive Them
description: The ninja team up with a reluctant Clutch Powers to enter a mysterious pyramid where they inadvertently unleash an ancient evil.

title: Lightfall Part 1
description: The mysterious Lord Obsidian calls Mega Man a traitor to robots and challenges him to a duel. An overconfident Mega Man is humbled by this mysterious new villain.

title: Balloon Boys
description: Vic & Val go on a hot air balloon trip with Sal and compete to be his favorite, but things go awry when they try to use the magical Nazca Lines to their advantage.

title: Silent Treatment/Sweet 'n' Sour
description: The Silent Treatment: When the girls go to see a silent movie with the Professor, they end up getting pulled into the film by an old-time villain./Sweet 'n' Sour: The girls must figure out how to beat Townsville's newest band of criminals: a group of adorable little animals.

title: Ben Again and Again
description: After Billy Billions' efforts to carve his face onto Mount Rushmore with a laser are thwarted by Ben, the billionaire brat turns his focus on removing Ben from the Omnitrix, but once he accidentally rips open a rift in space-time, the two must carefully navigate another timeline if they are to return to the present.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Escapism
description: Steven uses his psychic powers to find help.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Oportunidades laborales
description: Después de derrotar a Magnus, los Fantásticos reciben una oferta de empleo de alguien inesperado... Filomena Dusk.

title: Escape de Bahia Bebe
description: Cuando, por accidente, Vic y Val se convierten a sí mismos y a Don en bebés, deben escapar de una guardería para poder volver a sus edades normales.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Appleoni
description: Apple and Onion want credit for creating a new dance craze.

title: Compartir es querer
description: Courtney se niega a compartir su valioso juguete de coleccionista con sus amigos.

title: Superfriends
description: The new girl next door learns it's hard to be best friends with superheroes and soon starts hanging out with the wrong kind of kid, Princess.

title: El silencioso
description: Mientras que Lloyd y Harumi se aventuran a lo profundo de "Primeval's Eye" en busca de la tercer máscara Oni, los ninja tratan de arreglar al Bounty y hacer un descubrimiento sorprendente.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Trampas y Como Sobrevivir a Ellas
description: El ninja se une a un clutch Powers renuente para entrar en una misteriosa pirámide donde desatan sin darse cuenta un antiguo mal.

title: Tants
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to get back a gift that Pops gave them.

title: Power Up Puff
description: During a fight, both Buttercup and Bubbles are surprised to discover they've leveled up, leaving Blossom to wonder when or if she'll get new powers too.

title: Rush to Greatness
description: Rush puts his new battle upgrades to the test in a battle with Wave Man.

title: I Am My Monster
description: Everything is not fine.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Y todos nos llevamos bien
description: Owen y Beth tratan de salvar un hormiguero que Courtney y Leshawna quieren destruir.

title: Thunderhowl Part 1
description: Bumblebee and Chromia travel to Crystal City to recover one of Windblade's psychic shards and encounter a long-lost bot.

title: Safari Joe
description: While minding her own business, Cheetara is caught in a trap set by Safari Joe, the famously annoying hunter! After escaping, she rallies the other ThunderCats to help her stop Joe once and for all, by turning the tables and capturing him!

title: Cone in 60 Seconds
description: After Owen gets ripped off at the ice cream truck, the kids unite to right that wrong.

title: The Origins Part 2
description: Via the sewers, Darwin finds himself flushed out to sea. He is terrified but determined to make his way back to the Wattersons. However, a fish can't get very far on land so Darwin will have to do millions of years of evolution in a matter of hours if he's going to get home safe and sound.

title: Banda de por Vida
description: Cuando Vic y Val acompañan a Xochi a un concierto punk, quieren demostrar que son lo suficientemente geniales para salir con ella. Pero en un intento desesperado por tener onda, terminan arruinando el concierto.

title: Los Caza Chicos Malos
description: Izzqy quiere jugar un juego de superhéroes y está dispuesta a hacer lo que sea por ello.

title: The Bike Ride
description: Pizza Steve desperately tries to prevent the gang from finding out his shameful secret.

title: Swish
description: Namagem attacks Mega Man using a variety of powers, revealing that they both can replicate schematics. However, Namagem can carry more than three at a time! The true beginning of the mysterious villain's arc begins here.

title: Ninjago chico, problemas grandes
description: Los ninjas corres a salvar a Lloyd. Un Lord Garmadon más poderoso que nunca, crea una enorme estatua para ayudarlo a gobernar Ninjago y a derrotar a los ninjas.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Familiar
description: With many changes going on in his life, Steven tries to find his place in the world.

title: Ye Olde Laser Duel
description: As team Tennyson admires the efficiency of a super modern train station, Ben is quick to sniff out one of Steam Smythe's robots holding up the line. Once the fed up villain tricks our hero into accepting a duel, the fate of the Omnitrix hangs in the balance and it's up to Ben to set things right.

title: Secret in a Bottle
description: Craig needs to get a secret off his chest, so he pays a visit to the Keeper of Secrets in the Creek.

title: Juego de mascaras
description: Mientras Lloyd y Harumi buscan el templo Oni para la última máscara, los ninjas son tomados como rehenes y descubren que verdaderas intensiones de la Princesa Harumi.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Un experimento fallido
description: El plan de Filomena Dusk para redireccionar la energía de la Célula Núcleo fracasa, y Los Fantásticos deben pelear contra sus propios compañeros de trabajo dentro de las instalaciones de AAAnimus.

title: Homeworld Bound
description: Steven heads to the Diamonds for advice on how to control his new powers.

title: The Potion
description: Gumball and Darwin learn that Hector is not so happy being giant-sized. So they decide to help him by creating a potion that will shrink him down to the size of an average person. However creating a magic potion is not as easy as it sounds, and the results can go spectacularly wrong...

title: Frenos
description: Cuando los Osos van al dentista, Panda se coloca frenos. Pronto, descubre que los frenos le confieren habilidades superiores y ese poder se le sube a la cabeza.

title: La Banda Pizzera
description: Los Osos van a comer a la Cabaña de la Pizza de Papá Oso y terminan reemplazando la banda animatrónica del local. iSon tan exitosos que terminan saliendo de gira!

title: The Boxcurse Children
description: Clarence, Jeff, and Sumo stumble upon a mysterious box. After they open it, some strange things begin to happen. Convinced they've unlocked a curse, they become determined to reverse it!

title: Pony Tale
description: Uncle Grandpa grows a ponytail, which gains him the attention of a magical pony.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Meet Tygra
description: The smartest Thundercat, Tygra. Tygra's mission is to make Lion-O a better leader. He might get around to it too, if he wasn't so busy cleaning up after the other Thundercats.

title: Braces
description: When the Bears go to the dentist, Panda gets braces. But, Panda finds out his braces grant him super abilities and the power goes to his head.

title: El Gran Robo de Bongos
description: Los chicos olvidan conseguir un regalo para Chata en el Día de la Abuela y en un movimiento desesperado, le regalan los bongos que pidieron prestados a Xochi. Sabiendo que deben devolver los tambores, Victor y Valentino fingen ser ladrones para robar los instrumentos.

title: High Flying Hostiles/Backfire Brawl
description: High Flying Hostiles: While escorting the Mind Core Cell to AAAnimus Campus, the AO are attacked by Masato Kazami and his Body Guards./Backfire Brawl: Philomena's attempt to refocus the Mind Core Cell's power backfires and the AO must fight their fellow employees inside the AAAnimus Campus.

title: El joven y la logica
description: K.O. descubre cómo el Sr. Lógica llegó a la Plaza.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Sumo Goes West
description: Clarence learns his best friend Sumo may transfer to another school! It's up to Clarence to protest, petition and rally to convince everyone to let Sumo stay - or face losing his closest school pal!

title: Fright Wig
description: When the King cannot overcome his fears, he abuses having the Sheriff's Dept. on call.

title: Peluca de terror
description: Cuando el rey no logra superar sus miedos, se abusa de la ventaja que le da tener al departamento del sheriff de guardia.

title: Adopted
description: The Baby Bears get adopted by an eccentric millionaire and get to live in his mansion.

title: La Gran Fiebre de Fosiles
description: JP encuentra un fósil en el Arroyo, lo que causa que el paisaje cambie rápidamente.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Monster Party
description: Enid is faced with a choice when her old friends from Ghoul School show up.

title: The Trojan Bear
description: When Axel opens a subscription gift-box he didn't even order, the team finds their ranks divided by a robotic bear - or Princess SugarSalt in disguise!

title: Delivery Effect
description: Unikitty and gang have ordered some delicious Thai food for dinner.  Unfortunately the wait for the delivery is proving too much, time itself seems to have slowed down. In an effort to get the food their faster the gang utilizes Dr. Fox's time machine, which causes big problems and really hurts Father Time's feelings.

title: Change Your Mind
description: Steven faces his biggest challenge yet.

title: Escape From Earth Part 2
description: With the Ark extricated from Mt. St. Hilary, the Autobots must run the gauntlet of Decepticon forces to escape Earth with the Allspark.

title: King Koil
description: Ben and Gwen spend the day volunteering at Repto Ranch and come face to face with King Koil, but need to quickly overcome their fear of snakes if they are to rescue the released critters and defeat the slithery baddie.

title: King of the Zombeez
description: Frostferatu hires the Warriors to rid his castle of Zombeez when Neddy and a power mad zombie-bee queen take over.

title: Escapismo
description: Steven usa sus poderes psíquicos para conseguir ayuda.

title: Band For Life
description: When Vic and Val tag along with Xochi to a punk concert, they want to prove that they're cool enough to hang out with her. But in a desperate attempt to be cool, they wind up destroying the concert.

title: #ElFlechazo
description: Diana Prince está triunfando en todos los aspectos de la vida y como alumna de la Secundaria Metrópolis... hasta que alguien llega para confundirla totalmente.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Perdiendo el control
description: Después de más intentos fallidos por aprovechar la energía la Célula núcleo, Los Fantásticos deben pelear contra sus propios Bakugan usando tecnología AAAnimus para salvarlos.

title: Pizza Band
description: The Bears get pizza at Papa Bear's Pizza Cave and wind up replacing the place's animatronic band. They're such a hit that they go on tour!

title: Show de momias
description: Duncan sale en una misión para espantar a Courtney durante una excursión al museo.

title: Islands Part 4: Imaginary Resources
description: Finn and Jake travel to a land where reality has been redesigned and improved.

title: Ben una y otra vez
description: Cuando los esfuerzos de Billy Billiones por tallar su cara en el Monte Rushmore con un láser se ven frustrados por Ben, el malcriado multimillonario se concentra en sacar a Ben del Omnitrix. Pero cuando, por accidente, abre una grieta espacio-temporal, ambos deben navegar con cuidado por otra línea de tiempo si quieren regresar al presente.

title: The News Never Sleeps!
description: Lil' Nelson takes a job as a paperboy, which is more difficult than it sounds in a city overrun by scorching Pyro Vipers and an evil Serpentine sorceress.

title: Doble Hex
description: Mientras observan aves en el Parque Nacional Pinnacles, Gwen y Ben comienzan a competir para ver quién puede avistar más aves primero. Pero cuando el fuego del bosque interrumpe su diversión, el equipo Tennyson debe darse prisa para salvar a la población de aves y descubrir quién está detrás del fuego que crece sospechosamente: iHex!

title: Radical Rescue
description: Rad is forced to reconsider his identity when KO starts taking on some of his traits.

title: The Visitor
description: A mysterious alien named Xylene shows up and wants to return the Omnitrix to its rightful owner, Grandpa Max!

title: Here Comes Haavik/The Fusion Bakugan Arrive
description: Here Comes Haavik: An evil shapeshifting alien has landed in Los Volmos! If that wasn't bad enough, he has a group of robot mechanoids on his trail trying to bring him justice. Meanwhile, Dan has accepted a battle challenge from a pair of brawlers, Chad and Trey./The Fusion Bakugan Arrive: Still humiliated by their defeat, Chad and Trey challenge Dan to rematch but this time they have a few tricks up their sleeve, and a little help on their side.

title: Dia de elecciones
description: En un esfuerzo por demostrarle a Master Frown que no es una tirana, Unikitty acuerda celebrar una elección para ver quién será la nueva princesa del Unireino. En una situación sorpresiva, Master Frown toma una ventaja temprana en las encuestas. Unikitty descubre que Frown gana porque está haciendo trampa. ¿Recurrirá Unikitty a sus propios trucos sucios para ganar las elecciones o permanecerá fiel a sí misma y seguirá tratando de ganar gracias a su amabilidad?

title: Uncle Dummy
description: Uncle Grandpa and Pizza Steve try to convince Mr. Gus that his ventriloquist dummy is alive.

title: El verdadero potencial
description: Justo cuando los ninjas piensan que han salvado el día, Lord Garmadon regresa a Ninjago, y libera a Harumi, quien lo anima a "alcanzar su verdadero potencial" conquistando lo único que siempre se interpuso en su camino, su hijo, Lloyd.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Summer Fun Day!
description: The Thundercats are exhausted from fighting bad guys all the time so Lion-O suggests they spend a relaxing summer fun day at the beach, with no fighting! Unfortunately the beach is home to the Crabmen, giant, clawed humanoids that fight anyone who steps on their sand! Looks like summer fun day might involve some fighting!

title: La Pocion
description: Gumball y Darwin usan una poción mágica para encoger a Héctor.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: Collect Them All
description: After the other Titans are turned into collectibles and disappear, Robin must search yard sales and stores to find them.

title: Repulse!
description: Luthor infects Superman with a magnetic charge that repels everything. As the repulsing charge grows, the Magnetized Man of Steel is fated to spend the rest of his life isolated in space unless the Justice League can figure out a way to free him.

title: Legs from Here to Homeworld
description: Steven travels to visit family.

title: Sharing Is Caring
description: Courtney refuses to share her valuable collectors item toy with her classmates.

title: Sofa cama
description: Cuando los Piratas del Cielo se infiltran en el cuartel general del sheriff, iponen en peligro a los héroes!

title: Party Down Part 1
description: On their way to back to Cybertron, the Autobots attempt to have some well-deserved fun by throwing a party.

title: The Quiet One
description: As Lloyd and Harumi venture deep into Primeval's Eye in search of the third Oni Mask, the ninja attempt to fix the Bounty and make a startling discovery.

title: Christmas Movies
description: On Christmas Eve, the Baby Bears defend a video store from getting robbed.

title: Paint Job
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to paint a house.

title: Ninos de Globo
description: Vic y Val salen de viaje en globo aerostático con Sal y compiten por ser su favorito, pero las cosas se complican cuando tratan de usar las mágicas líneas de Nazca a su favor.

title: Enter the Wood Man
description: Mega Man accidentally awakens Wood Man, who thinks it's still the Hard Age, sets off on a path of destruction toward Silicon City.

title: Speed Demon
description: Batman has to enlist the help of Jason Blood, aka the Demon, when Brother Blood turns the Batmobile into a sentient, demonic entity.

title: Quips
description: Skips has to tell his cousin Tips to stop telling bad jokes.

title: Primer Vuelo
description: Cuando la banda hace un viaje en avión, Halcondrilo está al mando ya que hoy da el examen para obtener su licencia de capitán. Como a Richard le da terror volar, Unikitty y Perricornio pasan el caótico vuelo tratando de ayudarlo a vencer su miedo, mientras la Dra. Fox acompaña a Halcondrilo en la cabina para ayudarlo a aprobar su examen.

title: Small World: Abra-Disaster Part 1
description: After defeating Mojo for the umpteenth time, the Powerpuff Girls are confident they are unstoppable.

title: Sleeper Sofa
description: When the Sky Pirates infiltrate Sheriff HQ, they put our heroes in danger!

title: Superman Red vs Superman Blue
description: Luthor comes up with the means to separate each Justice Leaguer in two, one passive and good, the other aggressive and mean.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin necesita encontrar una foto de Clayton para ponerla en la portada del anuario escolar... ipero comete el error de pedirle ayuda de Tobías, que está interesado en aparecer en la portada!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Meet The Thunderkittens
description: The Thunderkittens might be the youngest Thundercats, but Wilykit and Wilykat are a dynamic brother and sister duo! They'll help take down any foe, even if they don't really know what their own capsule weapons can do.

title: Enemigos en el aire
description: Cuando Los Fantásticos transportan la Célula Núcleo a las instalaciones de AAAnimus, son atacados por Masato Kazami y sus Guardaespaldas.

title: Maestros
description: Cuando Darwin les pregunta a sus amigos qué profesor merece estar en la portada del anuario, iles cuesta encontrar a un solo candidato digno!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Future
description: Steven is finally ready to move on.

title: Escape From Earth Part 1
description: Optimus struggles to recover from using the Matrix of Leadership while the Autobots attempt to get the Allspark back to Cybertron.

title: Escape From Bebe Bay
description: When Vic & Val accidentally turn themselves and Don into babies, they must escape a daycare center in order to change back to their normal ages.

title: Wiped Out Part 2
description: Separated from his friends, Cheetor is captured by the territorial Sharkticons who enlist him in their fight over the last remaining bits of their destroyed planet.

title: El Antiguo Duelo Laser
description: Mientras el equipo Tennyson admira la eficiencia de una estación de tren súper moderna, Ben olfatea rápidamente a uno de los robots de Vapor Smythe, que está demorándose más de la cuenta. Pero cuando el villano, harto de esperar, engaña a nuestro héroe para que acepte un duelo, el destino del Omnitrix está en la cuerda floja y Ben es el encargado de arreglar las cosas.

title: Falafel en la carcel
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben sacar a Falafel de la cárcel por un delito que no cometió.

title: Stuck on You
description: Kybher, aided by a booger-like slime biot named Skurd, attacks Ben & co, but the tables turn when Skurd gloms onto Ben!

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: Dunklecorn
description: A mysterious relative, Uncle Donklecorn, shows up unexpectedly, claiming to be family. Hawkodile thinks it's just Master Frown and Brock in a donkey costume, trying to ruin things as usual, but Unikitty and Puppycorn are convinced Donklecorn is an old family member. Hawk follows his bodyguard senses and tries to prove that Donklecorn is a fake, until finally the real Master Frown and Brock show up and ruin things, just as he suspected they would. He admits he was wrong about Uncle Donklecorn, but all is forgiven and the friends dance it out together.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin se propone encontrar una foto de Carrie para la portada del anuario escolar, pero ambos terminan recordando todas sus travesuras espeluznantes del pasado.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Rage of the Red Lanterns
description: Chased by the Red Lanterns, Lobo seeks sanctuary with the Justice League. As the League attempts to stave off the Red Lanterns, Lobo reveals the real reason he wants shelter in the Watchtower, he wants access to a powerful space weapon being held by our heroes.

title: Juntos Solos
description: Steven organiza una fiesta para reunir a su familia.

title: Piernas del Planeta Madre
description: Steven viaja para visitar a su familia.

title: Mortimor to the Rescue
description: When Craig, Kelsey and JP get stranded in murky water, it's up to Mortimor to save the day!

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: The Points
description: Gumball and Darwin discover Tobias is doing way better than them in an online game called Galatrek. Tobias admits he earns good points doing chores for his parents, which he then exchanges for dollars to buy cool stuff for Galatrek. If Gumball and Darwin do Tobias' chores they can earn his good points and use them for Galatrek. Gumball and Darwin think they've hit the jackpot. But these good points may not be quite as good as Tobias claims.

title: El Misterio de la Guardiana del Tiempo
description: Cuando la Guardiana del Tiempo desaparece, Craig y sus amigos asumen la tarea de ayudar a otros niños a llegar a casa a tiempo para la cena.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Helado en 60 segundos
description: Después de que a Owen lo engañan en un camión de helados, los niños se unen para solucionarlo.

title: She Wore Red Velvet
description: When Booster and the JLA come under attack by a mysterious and unrelenting new villainess known as Red Velvet, Booster comes to realize she's actually the fiance he left at the altar in the future.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin le pide a Sarah una foto para poner en la portada del anuario escolar. Pero cuando Sarah trata de ayudar, las cosas se complican un poco.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Capture the Flag
description: Water balloon fights, warring factions and the risk of jail time, everything is on the line when Clarence and friends play the biggest game of capture the flag yet! Everyone wants to take home the crown, and the power to control the neighborhood's juice boxes.

title: Islands Part 3: Mysterious Island
description: After waking up alone and shipwrecked, Finn investigates a bizarre island in search of his friends.

title: Hot Garbage
description: When the Titans try to get Beast Boy to clean his room, they discover that there's more to garbage than just trash.

title: Guillermo's Gathering
description: When Vic & Val are forced to go to Guillermo's boring birthday party, they devise a scheme to leave early, but end up discovering that the party is way cooler than they thought.

title: Campamento Unikitty
description: La pandilla está lista para un fin de semana increíble, para vivir la buena vida acampando con estilo en la divertida y amigable naturaleza. Pero cuando Halcondrilo desafía su idea de acampar (debería ser una lucha por la supervivencia en los bosques hostiles), la pandilla intercambia el lugar con él: ahora, Halcondrilo vive una vida de campamento glamoroso mientras Unikitty y los otros sobreviven en la naturaleza. ¿Seguirá creyendo Unikitty que la "increíble naturaleza" es tan increíble si encuentran su destrucción por causas naturales?

title: Thirst for Power
description: Axel and his toys deploy the Joyride in a "ship" to "ship" battle against Dr. Nautilus, who has punctured a water main to flood the sewers and established himself as "Admiral Nautilus."

title: The Charm Offensive
description: After Ben gets too much publicity for his alien antics in Fort Knox, a jealous Gwen feels unappreciated and looks to ease her pain with ice cream, but once she is confronted by Charmcaster looking to avenge Michael Morningstar, Gwen must prove to herself she's a worthy member of Team Tennyson if they are to survive.

title: Familiar
description: Con tantos cambios en su vida, Steven intenta encontrar su lugar en el mundo.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Career Opportunities/Punch the Clock
description: Career Opportunities: After defeating Magnus the AO get an offer of employment from a surprising source Philomena Dusk!/Punch the Clock: During a commercial to celebrate their joining the AAAnimus team Dan and the AO rebel before they sellout.

title: Adoptados
description: Un millonario excéntrico adopta a los Osos bebé y los lleva a vivir a su mansión.

title: T.G.I.S
description: The Secret Saturdays come to Bellwood to investigate a rash of chupacabra attacks.

title: Manzallin
description: Manzana y Cebollín quieren llevarse el crédito de haber creado una nueva moda de baile.

title: Wild Wild Wheel Part 2
description: WildWheel finds Optimus Prime rebuilding a small Cybertronian town, only to discover the Prime does not recognize him.

title: Big Trouble, Little NinjaGo
description: The ninja race to save Lloyd, as a more powerful-than-ever Lord Garmadon creates an enormous Colossi to help him rule Ninjago and defeat the ninja.

title: La Fiesta de Guillermo
description: Cuando Vic y Val se ven forzados a ir a la aburrida fiesta de cumpleaños de Guillermo, crean un plan para irse temprano, pero terminan descubriendo que la fiesta es mucho mejor de lo que pensaban.

title: For the Love of Narwhal
description: Vambre rejects Darlin' Narwhal Magisword as being unfit for battle, but when Prohyas trains and brings out its full potential, Vambre resorts to improper extremes to get it back.

title: Las Noticias Nunca Duermen
description: Lil 'Nelson toma un trabajo como repartidor de periódicos, lo cual es más difícil de lo que parece en una ciudad invadida por Pyro Vipers y una malvada hechicera serpentina.

title: First Flight
description: The gang is taking an airplane trip together, and Hawk is at the helm since today he's taking his captain's license test. However Richard is terrified of flying, so Unikitty & Puppycorn spend the chaotic flight trying to help Rick conquer his fear of flying while Dr Fox joins Hawk in the cockpit to help him pass his test. After a destructive and dangerous flight, Rick makes it safetly back on the ground (after surviving the plane crashing). Hawk fails his test but gets to take it again next week, so the gang is excited for another free flight.

title: That's a Wrap
description: Duncan goes on a mission to scare Courtney during a field trip to the museum.

title: The Unnaturals
description: Ben learns that evil robots have replaced all the kids at the Little League World Series. And now they want to replace the President of the USA!

title: Election Day
description: In an effort to prove to Master Frown that she is no tyrant, Unikitty agrees to hold an election to see who will be the new princess of the Unikingdom. In a shock, Master Frown takes an early lead in the poles. Unikitty discovers Frown is winning because he's cheating. Will she resort to her own dirty tricks to win the election or stay true to her self and try to win by being nice?

title: #NoDerribenElArbol
description: Jessica Cruz y Pam Isley se unen para evitar que un antiguo árbol sea talado, pero ninguna se da cuenta de quien es el alter ego de la otra ni los extremos a los que llegarán para proteger lo que es importante.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Alan
description: Darwin quiere poner a Alan en la portada del anuario escolar, pero la aparente modestia de Alan se interpone.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Secret of the Omnitrix Part 2
description: In a battle with Animo, Ben in hero mode, doesn't listen to reason from Max and Gwen, and gets engulfed in a weird energy light. Little does Ben know that the "self destruct" function on the Omnitrix has just been initiated!

title: Thank You for Watching the Show
description: When KO finds moments of his life slipping by, he begins to suspect something weird is going on.

title: Rey Koil
description: Ben y Gwen pasan el día como voluntarios en Repto Ranch y se enfrentan cara a cara con el Rey Koil. Pero necesitan superar rápidamente su miedo a las serpientes si quieren rescatar a las criaturas liberadas y derrotar al serpenteante villano.

title: Salamander
description: When the professor is kidnapped, the girls must go to a mysterious island to save him.

title: Dread on Arrival
description: The ninja appeal to the police commissioner of Ninjago in an effort to help save Lloyd and thwart Harumi's efforts to resurrect the evil Lord Garmadon.

title: #CrushingIt
description: Diana Prince is absolutely crushing it in every single aspect of life as a student at Metropolis High, until someone shows up who threatens to throw her off her game for good.

title: Un nuevo empleo
description: Durante un comercial para celebrar su contrato con el equipo AAAnimus, Dan y Los Fantásticos deciden rebelarse antes que traicionar sus principios.

title: Thunderhowl Part 2
description: Released after eons of imprisonment, Thunderhowl helps Bee and Chromia navigate the dangerous Crystal City.

title: Tongue Tied
description: Uncle Grandpa helps a shy kid gain confidence.

title: Presidential Punchout
description: When Morbucks enters the Student Body President race, Blossom sinks to her level to secure the win.

title: Wiped Out Part 1
description: Out in space to catch some solar waves, Bumblebee, Hot Rod and Cheetor discover the asteroid remains of a mysterious planet.

title: Seed No Evil/City of Clipsville
description: Seed No Evil: When a prehistoric caveman thaws out in Townsville, the girls must stop him from stealing the Mayor's seeds./City of Clipsville: The girls reminisce on their adventures in these new, never-before-seen clips!

title: Acompanantes
description: Para poder dormir un poco, los Osos ayudan a un ave molesta a encontrar una nueva pareja.

title: Like Water for Bimm
description: Vambre helps to get Bimm over her mission crippling fear of water.

title: Wingmen
description: In order to get some sleep, the Bears help an annoying bird find a new mate.

title: Terror llegando
description: Los ninjas recurren al comisionado de la policía de Ninjago en un esfuerzo por ayudar a salvar a Lloyd y frustrar los esfuerzos de Harumi de resucitar al malvado Lord Garmadon.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: The Great Fossil Rush
description: JP finds a fossil in the Creek which quickly causes the landscape to change.
